  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Package of support for students who have to defer their studies
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Details on a range of opportunities to gain new skills, undertake work placements, additional learning and career development support. </p>

  </div>
